explanation: [0-0] A man with a beard and blonde hair, wearing red, sits at a table and uses chopsticks to pick up noodles from a green bowl. Behind him is a blue wall with a painting, and to his right, a cabinet with other items on it.

[0-10] The man in red stretches out the chopsticks. The scene changes to the chopsticks reaching the mouth of a person wearing pink baby clothes and a pink butterfly on their head. This person sits in a white chair, with a refrigerator and cabinets behind them. They open their mouth, eat the noodles, and then spit them onto the face of the man in red. The scene changes again to show the spit-out noodles falling to the ground, where a person dressed as a cockroach stands. The cockroach person walks toward the noodles on the ground. At this moment, the man in red bends down to clean up the noodles. The scene changes back to the person wearing the pink butterfly, who is crying. Then, a white toy is stuffed into their mouth. They look at it and spit it out. The scene cuts to the toy falling on the ground, with the cockroach person walking towards it.
